Grammar

    0 $accept: Program $end

    1 Program: Decls

    2 Decls: Decls Decl
    3      | ε

    4 Decl: FuncDecl
    5     | VarDecl
    6     | TypeDecl

    7 FuncDecl: VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON
    8         | VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES FuncBody

    9 FuncBody: LBRACE Stmts RBRACE

   10 VarDecl: VarType VarList SEMICOLON

   11 TypeDecl: _VarType SEMICOLON

   12 VarType: _VarType
   13        | CONST _VarType

   14 _VarType: BuiltinType
   15         | STRUCT IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE
   16         | UNION IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE
   17         | ENUM IDENTIFIER LBRACE EnumList RBRACE
   18         | _VarType ASTERISK
   19         | IDENTIFIER

   20 VarList: VarList COMMA VarInit
   21        | VarInit
   22        | ε

   23 VarInit: IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList
   24        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN Expr
   25        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN LBRACE InitList RBRACE
   26        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN LBRACE RBRACE

   27 InitList: InitList COMMA Expr
   28         | Expr

   29 ArrayBoundList: ArrayBoundList ArrayBound
   30               | ArrayBound
   31               | ε

   32 ArrayBound: LBRACKET INTEGER RBRACKET

   33 ParamList: ParamList COMMA Param
   34          | ParamList COMMA ELLIPSES
   35          | Param
   36          | ELLIPSES
   37          | ε

   38 Param: VarType IDENTIFIER
   39      | VarType

   40 BuiltinType: CHAR
   41            | SHORT
   42            | INT
   43            | LONG
   44            | UNSIGNED
   45            | UNSIGNED CHAR
   46            | UNSIGNED SHORT
   47            | UNSIGNED INT
   48            | UNSIGNED LONG
   49            | FLOAT
   50            | DOUBLE
   51            | BOOL
   52            | VOID

   53 FieldDecls: FieldDecls FieldDecl
   54           | ε

   55 FieldDecl: VarType MemberList SEMICOLON
   56          | SEMICOLON

   57 MemberList: MemberList COMMA IDENTIFIER
   58           | IDENTIFIER
   59           | ε

   60 EnumList: EnumList COMMA Enum
   61         | Enum
   62         | ε

   63 Enum: IDENTIFIER
   64     | IDENTIFIER ASSIGN INTEGER

   65 Stmts: Stmts Stmt
   66      | ε

   67 Stmt: Expr SEMICOLON
   68     | IfStmt
   69     | SwitchStmt
   70     | ForStmt
   71     | DoStmt
   72     | WhileStmt
   73     | ContinueStmt
   74     | BreakStmt
   75     | ReturnStmt
   76     | Block
   77     | TypeDecl
   78     | VarDecl
   79     | SEMICOLON

   80 IfStmt: IF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt ELSE Stmt
   81       | IF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   82 SwitchStmt: SWITCH LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES LBRACE CaseStmtList RBRACE

   83 CaseStmtList: CaseStmtList CaseStmt
   84             | ε

   85 CaseStmt: CASE Expr COLON Stmts
   86         | DEFAULT COLON Stmts

   87 ForStmt: FOR LPARENTHESES Expr SEMICOLON Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt
   88        | FOR LPARENTHESES SEMICOLON Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt
   89        | FOR LPARENTHESES VarDecl Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   90 DoStmt: DO Stmt WHILE LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON

   91 WhileStmt: WHILE LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   92 ContinueStmt: CONTINUE SEMICOLON

   93 BreakStmt: BREAK SEMICOLON

   94 ReturnStmt: RETURN SEMICOLON
   95           | RETURN Expr SEMICOLON

   96 Block: LBRACE Stmts RBRACE

   97 Expr: IDENTIFIER
   98     | Constant
   99     | LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES
  100     | Expr COMMA Expr
  101     | IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ExprList RPARENTHESES
  102     | Expr DOT IDENTIFIER
  103     | Expr ARROW IDENTIFIER
  104     | Expr LBRACKET Expr RBRACKET
